journalist, Kemi Olunloyo has claimed that Deji Adeleke, billionaire businessman who is the father of superstar music artist, Davido is expecting a child soon. Kemi Olunloyo made this known, on Wednesday through her Twitter handle saying the recent granddad is preparing for the arrival of a child with his girlfriend and the young lady, still unknown, has been sent to America to deliver her baby. She tweeted: “So happy for #BabaOlowo Deji Adeleke expecting a baby soon with his girlfriend. This lovely young lady in her late 20’s has been sent to America to coop like Chioma cooped in UK. Davido gets double joy. New baby & new sibling in 12 mos. For the baba ke! A new OBO.” Source